            Implementation Roundtable
        .panel-body
          Software automation has many faces, from locally-run functional and unit tests, to server-driven continuous integration, and even external device farms. How do you do automated testing in your team? What works well for you? More interestingly, what didn't work and why? Come talk implementation details with other professional developers. We don't care about your platform, your budget or your team size; we just want to hear your story.
        .panel-footer
          View and comment on topic suggestions at implementation.autotestingroundtable.com, and suggest new ones via implementation@autotestingroundtable.com. 
