        .panel-heading
          %h3
            Process Roundtable
        .panel-body
          Beyond the software that we use to test our games are the people that write the tests and the workflows they use to reinforce them. How does the process work in your studio? Are the engineers responsbile for automated tests, or QA? Are QA silo'd or intergrated? We don't care about your platform, your budget or your team size; we just want to hear your story.
        .panel-footer
          View and comment on topic suggestions at process.autotestingroundtable.com, and suggest new ones via process@autotestingroundtable.com. 
